llinois Medical District (IMD) on our west side of campus to medical students visiting Chicago.  This option is available for visiting medical students that are working on:   medical rotations  externships  electives        Summer Guest and Conference Accommodations - May 24, 2020, through August 9, 2020   Intern Housing  UIC hosts students from around the world who are completing their summer internships in Chicago. Our convenient location near downtown Chicago and along public transit routes makes commuting easy for these students with access to the CTA buses and train lines.  Past interns staying at UIC have completed internships with the following companies/organizations:   Tyson Foods  FH Paschen  Hillshire Farms  Deloitte  Walgreens  UNCF  Chicago Fire – MLS Soccer   Conference Housing  Campus Housing offers housing options to both small and large conference groups facilitating their activities both on and off the UIC campus.  We offer both single and double occupancy rooms in air-conditioned residence halls throughout our east, south, and west sides of campus.  Our facilities offer:   traditional-style rooms with a community bathroom on each floor  cluster-style rooms are a combination of single and double occupancy units which share a small cluster bathroom within their own private suite  suite style is the same as a cluster with the addition of a shared living space  apartment-style units provide everyone with their own private bedroom, sharing the common spaces within the unit             GUESTS AND CONFERENCES    Back to main content           Guest Housing    Medical Students    Intern Housing    Conference Housing     Resources                    UIC Logo        Campus Housing         Future    Apply    Housing Rates    Residence Halls    Services    Why Live on Campus      Current    Apply    Summer Housing    Housing During Breaks    Academic Support    Get Involved    Services      GUESTS AND CONFERENCES    Conference Housing    Guest Housing    Inte